snippet.textDisplay: Aside from the obvious good words about the very very well written lyrics, music and precision of the artistic setting (the whole stage, dresses, designs); a special shoutout to Coke studio for making it possible. To bring out a song purely for 'Bangladeshi' people...on a matter that everyone can strongly relate to, in dialects dear to people of this region. Also for bringing out fresh voices...the three singers even though moderately popular before, to showcase their talent on such a premium studio/art direction...it must have been amazing and it is also refreshing to see the youth taking an interest and being creative with our art, culture and tradition.
